race.description: Share Bets With Tabtouch Bet Loop Handicap
race.comment: FLINDERS LANE (2) is another strong winning chance for the top hoop. She stepped up to this distance at Ascot and was straight back into the winners' list. Has been kept on the fresh side and is well placed to keep the ball rolling. ETERNAL ROMANCE (14)  also lifted to this trip when missing a long neck at Ascot. Spiked her figures and will be right in it, holding that form. AL UNIQUE (9) was sharply better in that contest when finishing a whisker behind the above. He also ran on strongly from the back and draws much better today. MODELISTIC (8) contested that contest and ran into it well when missing by 1.4L. Is busting to win but will need some luck from an outside alley. ROYAL TROOPER (3) has good ability and won't be far away up in trip.
